Project Context: CS5344 Project - Longitudinal Data RUL Prediction.
Goal: Build ONE transferable pipeline for both SCANIA (trucks) and Backblaze (hard drives).
Key Constraints:

Evaluation: Cost-sensitive. Late alarms are much more expensive than early alarms.

Labels: Binned ordinal RUL classes (0, 1, 2, 3, 4 for Scania; 0, 1, 2 for Backblaze).

Format: Longitudinal data with variable length sequences.

Coding Style: Modular Python with Type Hints (Java-style rigor). Use UniversalAdapter to unify column names.